snippet.textDisplay: In the last dev stream they said, and I quot, "We like to leave crumbs behind for you to figure out." I think, they are tricking us again, and will give us two legends! this is the theory, in the picture behind forge, he has no scar, green eyes, and on his robotic arm the eye looking bits are big and long. in the animation, they are round, he has brown eyes, and a scar on his eye. i think that this isnt the real forge, but a double that looks like him. since he is a several times champion and sponcered by hammond robotics, I think if he is going somewhere un-safe, they will use a guy that looks simular. also, in his death box in the sorting factory it says "often imitated" so i think he is still alive and healthy.
